  "title": "Restaurant Supervisor/ Orchard/ 5 Days/ Japanese Restaurant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p><p> 44 hours per week</p><p><strong>Work Days:</strong></p><p> 5 days work, 2 off days </p><p><strong>Meals:</strong></p><p> Provided</p><p><strong>Location: </strong></p><p>Orchard,<br /><br /><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Assist Restaurant Manager with daily outlet operations</p></li><li><p>Open and close the outlet according to checklist</p></li><li><p>Supervise service staff and guide new team members</p></li><li><p>Deliver excellent customer service and handle feedback professionally</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with kitchen team to ensure smooth service flow</p></li><li><p>Handle cash, POS transactions, and daily sales reporting</p></li><li><p>Monitor stock, ingredients, and bar items (FIFO & par level)</p></li><li><p>Ensure food safety, hygiene, and cleanliness standards (SFA compliant)</p></li><li><p>Maintain outlet safety and service standards</p></li><li><p>Perform other duties as assigned</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Strong leadership, positive attitude, and customer-focused</li><li>Able to work well in a team<br /></li></ul><p>If you are interested, please send your resume to lucas.chang@swiftsearchglobal.com or whatsapp/call - 9339 2324</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Lucas Chang<br />EA Personnel No: R1874043<br />EA License No: 18C9495<br /></p>",
